 generalised Drinfeld associators on the punctured Riemann sphere are\nhypergeometric functions. We also study single-valued versions of these\nhypergeometric functions, which may be of independent interest.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 16:59:38 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 21 Apr 2020 15:41:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-23"}
