\norgan-average TIA as obtained by conventional whole-organ evaluation.\nUnfortunately, we did not have ground-truth TIA of our patient data and proper\nground-truth could even be impossible to obtain. Nevertheless, there are strong\nindicators that Particle Filtering can be used for reducing voxel-wise TAC\nnoise.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 15 Jul 2019 17:26:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-16"}
