ent with\nZF that the Lebesgue measure is not sigma-additive, Easwaran is thereby walking\nback his earlier endorsement. We note a related inaccuracy in the textbook\nMeasure Theory by Paul Halmos.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 16 Jul 2019 14:44:32 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 30 Jul 2019 08:28:34 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-07-31"}
